{"tid":650684,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"90's Telegram Group","createTime":"2018-05-02T14:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T15:18:58.000Z","uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ea60069529d1d748142695b14391df44fad6f8","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:21:02.000Z","msg":"開左個TG Group. 有私隱得來其實都唔係話勁有私隱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎90後各行各業嘅各位一齊入來吹下水傾下計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我們希望關系和諧，因始沒有你我之分，更沒有兩登之分<br />\n<br />\n90's Telegram Group為會員而設，暫時只限相關會員加入<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nGroup內比較著重繁體字及廣東話文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果對呢方面保有獨特嘅執著請勿申請<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麻煩填一填表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n表格會開到5月9日，填妥表格後會收到一封確認電郵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收集左各位巴打反映表格收集太多個人資料，所以已經進行簡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但部份保障措施必不可少：同意所有條款後會需求輸入電話號號作收取入Group連結用途，此舉係希望確保表格均為本人有填寫及意識下同意條款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScdlZMWvaXQT6lNdjFwVzjE629Dx4gpTbyt7cgZnpkc2FqfWg/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScdlZMWvaXQT6lNdjFwVzjE629Dx4gpTbyt7cgZnpkc2FqfWg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=qAXHMD4f4%2FwvA6TmMjB1HAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=e3a9fc08\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScdlZMWvaXQT6lNdjFwVzjE629Dx4gpTbyt7cgZnpkc2FqfWg/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n香港好危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家傾計傾得開心又放心"},{"pid":"8b939ae08aa066ec740559c085a02e2d1a955f15","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T14:31:52.000Z","msg":"關<del>系</del> 係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n開多個po唔好意思"},{"pid":"6d1d54fa629f571fb8e5a725ac004ab7e5d3b764","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-02T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"215c79b6097a005cdfbe61773578c2b43d6a31ab","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T00:17:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e95f948c8abd4442274b19795c0a88ea372497","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:15:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f90471971adc817ae3611780988d9d6f8bed7e5","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6186dde5b45ece2491a5637a0411a88edf56014b","tid":650684,"uid":180125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T15:18:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}